---
title: Spring Brunch Salad Serves 4 | with Goat Cheese and Herby Croutons
description: No brunch table is complete without a delicious salad, especially on Mother's Day, and this one has it all! Creamy goat cheese, perfectly cooked eggs, herby croutons, heirloom tomatoes, pickled shallots and crispy cucumber.
